# Repository Structure and Entry Points

This is a polyglot monorepo with three services. The main entry points per package are:

- frontend: [frontend/src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:frontend/src/app/layout.tsx) and Next.js App Router pages under [frontend/src/app](mdc:frontend/src/app)
- backend: Spring Boot application under [backend/src/main/java/com/ai/mes](mdc:backend/src/main/java/com/ai/mes), configuration in [backend/src/main/resources/application.yml](mdc:backend/src/main/resources/application.yml)
- ai-service: FastAPI app at [ai-service/app/main.py](mdc:ai-service/app/main.py)

Routing and composition:
- Frontend rewrites: [frontend/next.config.js](mdc:frontend/next.config.js) maps `/api/backend/*` to the Backend and `/api/ai/*` to the AI service
- Backend REST controllers (Swagger-annotated): [backend/src/main/java/com/ai/mes/controller](mdc:backend/src/main/java/com/ai/mes/controller)
- Backend MyBatis mappers: [backend/src/main/resources/mapper](mdc:backend/src/main/resources/mapper)

Build/Run:
- Root scripts: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- Frontend scripts and deps: [frontend/package.json](mdc:frontend/package.json)
- Backend build: [backend/pom.xml](mdc:backend/pom.xml)
- AI service deps: [ai-service/requirements.txt](mdc:ai-service/requirements.txt)